### What We Do
AI-powered patient assessment and contract generation platform for home care agencies. Staff records assessment interview on phone, AI transcribes in real time, generates assessment + care plan + service agreement, contract sent to client ready to sign. "One tap. AI handles the rest."

### The Problem
Agencies lose hours/week to manual documentation. Assessments hand-written after visits, contracts templated and generic, paperwork delays client onboarding.

### HIPAA Classification
Non-healthcare-only Business Associate of organizations subject to HIPAA. Palm Technologies provides general purpose products/services that may receive PHI from covered entities.

